8:22:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224241675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212624\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677313166\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022226229\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CrashPilot\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, CrashPilot said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthx mate can ur help with my camera problem in ksp2?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately, I am having the same issue, and do not know of a solution at this time. \u00A0Give it a day or two for other forum members to check in. \u00A0It\u0027s late at night in North America, so a lot of users are offline right now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TCAlex01","CreatedById":226105,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-25T08:44:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you try the tutorial? Right mouse button to rotate, mouse wheel to zoom, middle mouse button for up/down,\u00A0 middle mouse button on a part to focus on this part, home button to reset the camera?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FuelX","CreatedById":163054,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-25T13:38:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTCAlex explained it well. I want to add emphasis on middle mouse button. Not just scrolling the wheel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMiddle mouse button up/down, you have to press the button, keep it pressed and move the mouse up or down. Picture it like if you are dragging your rocket up and down.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMiddle mouse button click on a part to focus is the best. If the part your working on is in an akward position or orientation. Just middle click on it. It also works when you have parts of assemblies spread around in your \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CrashPilot","CreatedById":226229,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-25T20:05:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224241699\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212624\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677314651\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022226105\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TCAlex01\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, TCAlex01 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you try the tutorial? Right mouse button to rotate, mouse wheel to zoom, middle mouse button for up/down,\u00A0 middle mouse button on a part to focus on this part, home button to reset the camera?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthx i will try it i will update you tomorrow\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}